---
description: "Redux Toolkit patterns"
globs: ["src/store/**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use createSlice from Redux Toolkit
- Define interfaces for state types
- Use PayloadAction for typed actions
- Keep slices focused on a single domain
- Export actions and reducer from slice file

- Follow guide best practices https://redux.js.org/style-guide/
- Avoid Dispatching Many Actions Sequentially